Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.35,0:04:14.35,Default,Floof,0,0,0,,{TIME:253357,254358}Prepare?{NOTE:準備？}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.31,0:04:16.86,Default,Spex,0,0,0,,{TIME:255318,256861}Yes.{NOTE:そう…}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.86,0:04:19.61,Default,Spex,0,0,0,,{TIME:256861,259614}We need a strategy!{NOTE:作戦だゴロニャ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.03,0:04:25.36,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:263034,265369}Here you go, princess.{NOTE:ほらよ。捕らわれのお姫さま。}
