Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.95,0:04:30.50,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:267955,270500}Oops, you're right.{NOTE:おっとそうだったな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.50,0:04:33.25,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:270500,273252}Pardon my rudeness, little Rider girl.{NOTE:失礼。ライダーのお嬢ちゃん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.79,0:04:36.42,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:275797,276422}Oh?{NOTE:おっ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.38,0:04:39.13,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:277381,279133}Do I have something on my face?{NOTE:俺の顔に何かついてるか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.38,0:04:44.59,Default,Avinia,0,0,0,,{TIME:280384,284597}No. It's just… I'm not sure why, but…{NOTE:いえ。ただ自分でも不思議なんですが…}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.59,0:04:48.43,Default,Avinia,0,0,0,,{TIME:284597,288434}…I feel like we know each other from somewhere.{NOTE:…私はやっぱりあなたを知ってる気がするんです。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.43,0:04:50.97,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:288434,290978}Nah, I have a common face.{NOTE:いやぁ、よくある顔だから。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.97,0:04:54.56,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:290978,294565}Doesn't change how handsome I am, though.{NOTE:さらさらヘアーのイケメンってやつ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.56,0:04:56.06,Default,Avinia,0,0,0,,{TIME:294565,296067}It's not about your face.{NOTE:顔のことじゃありません。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.06,0:04:57.56,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:296067,297568}{NOTE:でっ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.56,0:04:59.11,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:297568,299111}I see…{NOTE:あっそ…}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.11,0:05:02.61,Default,Avinia,0,0,0,,{TIME:299111,302615}It's about that melody you're always humming.{NOTE:あなたの歌ってる歌のことです。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.20,0:05:07.91,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:305201,307912}That's a common melody.{NOTE:あれもよくある歌だ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.91,0:05:09.45,Default,Avinia,0,0,0,,{TIME:307912,309455}Is it really?{NOTE:本当でしょうか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.45,0:05:10.62,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:309455,310623}It is.{NOTE:本当さ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.79,0:05:16.79,Default,Nuts,0,0,0,,{TIME:312792,316796}Master Gale, Master Anvis called for you.{NOTE:ゲイルさま。アンヴィスさまがお呼びですよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.79,0:05:18.29,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:316796,318297}Geez…{NOTE:やれやれ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.29,0:05:20.63,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:318297,320633}Well, Master Anvis's orders are absolute.{NOTE:アンヴィスさまの命令は絶対だ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.34,0:05:26.76,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:322343,326764}And you'd better not do anything stupid in case something happens, little girl.{NOTE:お嬢ちゃんも何か起きても無茶しない方が身のためだぜ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.85,0:05:37.27,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:330852,337275}When we find the Black Castle, Lute and I will approach from the front and draw their attention.{NOTE:ブラックキャッスルを見つけたら俺とリュートが正面から突っ込んでやつらの注意を引く。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.27,0:05:40.19,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:337275,340194}In the mean time everyone else will infiltrate from the side.{NOTE:その隙に他のみんなはアジトに潜入。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.19,0:05:44.65,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:340194,344657}Our goal is to rescue Avinia and to find our Senior Riders' Kinship Stones.{NOTE:アユリアを助け出して先輩たちの絆石を見つけ出すんだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.65,0:05:45.74,Default,Hyoro,0,0,0,,{TIME:344657,345741}Got it.{NOTE:うん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.74,0:05:46.86,Default,Mille,0,0,0,,{TIME:345741,346868}Roger that.{NOTE:了解。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.86,0:05:48.03,Default,Nariki,0,0,0,,{TIME:346868,348035}I'll do my best!{NOTE:頑張るっす。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.74,0:05:50.83,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:348744,350830}Lute and I will keep the Ebon Riders busy.{NOTE:俺たちで四天王を何とかしよう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.83,0:05:51.83,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:350830,351831}Got it.{NOTE:ああ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.83,0:05:53.87,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:351831,353875}So we're leaving Avinia to you.{NOTE:アユリアのことを頼む。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.87,0:05:55.16,Default,Mille,0,0,0,,{TIME:353875,355167}You can count on us.{NOTE:任せといて。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.16,0:05:56.79,Default,Nariki,0,0,0,,{TIME:355167,356794}We'll rescue her in no time!{NOTE:やってやるっす。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.79,0:05:59.17,Default,Beats,0,0,0,,{TIME:356794,359171}Leave the support to us!{NOTE:援護は俺たちに任せとけ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.17,0:06:00.54,Default,(unison),0,0,0,,{TIME:359171,360548}– Yeah!\N– Yeah!{NOTE:—ああ！\\N—ええ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.38,0:06:04.76,Default,Anvis,0,0,0,,{TIME:363384,364760}Gale.{NOTE:ゲイルよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.76,0:06:07.43,Default,Anvis,0,0,0,,{TIME:364760,367430}How is that girl?{NOTE:あの娘の様子はどうだ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.43,0:06:11.22,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:367430,371225}How to put it… I don't think this is a case of stubbornness…{NOTE:いやぁ、頑固っていうか何ていうか。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.22,0:06:14.56,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:371225,374562}It looks like she really doesn't know about the secret art.{NOTE:秘術のことは何にも知らないんじゃないっすかね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.56,0:06:16.89,Default,Anvis,0,0,0,,{TIME:374562,376898}And what about you?{NOTE:ではお前はどうだ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.89,0:06:18.06,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:376898,378065}{NOTE:はっ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.06,0:06:19.27,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:378065,379275}Me…?{NOTE:俺っすか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.27,0:06:25.44,Default,Anvis,0,0,0,,{TIME:379275,385448}Is it just my imagination, or has the number of Kinship Stones you bring in dropped recently?{NOTE:絆石を持ってくる回数が減ったように思うが気のせいか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.57,0:06:29.07,Default,Nuts,0,0,0,,{TIME:386574,389076}I didn't say anything…!{NOTE:俺何も言ってないって…}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.07,0:06:30.28,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:389076,390286}Hmph.{NOTE:フン。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.24,0:06:33.53,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:391245,393539}I'm terribly sorry, Master Anvis!{NOTE:申し訳ありません、アンヴィスさま！}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.53,0:06:38.08,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:393539,398085}From today on, I'll double my efforts in hunting for Kinship Stones!{NOTE:今日からまたバリバリ絆石を狩りに行ってまいります！}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.42,0:06:43.71,Default,Wrath,0,0,0,,{TIME:400421,403716}As usual, he puts on a good show.{NOTE:相変わらず、調子のいい野郎だぜ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.71,0:06:44.59,Default,Shadow,0,0,0,,{TIME:403716,404592}Hmph.{NOTE:フン。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.59,0:06:47.01,Default,Shadow,0,0,0,,{TIME:404592,407011}Gale is pretty cunning.{NOTE:抜け目ないやつだよゲイルは。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.01,0:06:48.13,Default,Mad,0,0,0,,{TIME:407011,408137}Heh.{NOTE:フッ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.13,0:06:53.72,Default,Mad,0,0,0,,{TIME:408137,413726}Well, whatever the case may be, nothing escapes Master Anvis's eyes.{NOTE:いかなる者であってもアンヴィスさまの目をごまかすことはできません。}
