Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.03,0:07:12.74,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:431035,432745}Looks like there's no mistake.{NOTE:間違いなさそうだね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.95,0:07:17.50,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:433955,437500}Gale really was telling the truth.{NOTE:ゲイルの言ってたことは本当だったんだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.00,0:07:24.29,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:443005,444298}Gale!{NOTE:ゲイル！}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.84,0:07:29.09,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:447843,449095}Hey, hey!{NOTE:おいおい。}
