Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.68,0:07:36.72,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:453683,456727}And I told you not to.{NOTE:俺はやめとけと言ったはずだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.72,0:07:38.89,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:456727,458896}You'll just get beaten up.{NOTE:たたきのめされるだけだとな。}
