Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.11,0:07:50.78,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:468114,470783}We'll rescue Avinia no matter what!{NOTE:アユリアは絶対取り戻す！}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.78,0:07:52.45,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:470783,472451}Let's go, Cheval!{NOTE:行くぞシュヴァル！}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.45,0:07:53.45,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:472451,473452}Yeah!{NOTE:ああ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.45,0:07:54.66,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:473452,474662}Ride On!{NOTE:ライドオン！}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.87,0:07:58.04,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:476872,478040}Rathalos!{NOTE:リオレウス！}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.49,0:07:59.66,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:478499,479667}Ride On!{NOTE:ライドオン！}
