Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.46,0:08:12.51,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:488467,492513}Your heroic self-sacrifice will not go to waste!{NOTE:お前の英雄的自己犠牲無駄にはしないぞ～！}
