Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.10,0:09:42.22,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:581102,582228}Ratha!{NOTE:レウス！}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.44,0:09:50.19,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:588442,590194}You're pretty good.{NOTE:やるじゃん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.19,0:09:51.94,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:590194,591946}Ratha! Get rid of him!{NOTE:レウス！追っ払うんだ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.57,0:09:53.65,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:592571,593656}Heh.{NOTE:フッ…}
